20.1.3 Effects Analysis

Chosen model: Gamma (‘log’) 
```{r}
glmmTMB(formula = A_ML ~ Condition * Z + (1 | Mouse), data = data, 
    family = Gamma("log"), REML = TRUE, ziformula = ~0, dispformula = ~1)
```
